# Delegation Preference

The user prefers the agent to carry out operational steps directly instead of asking them to run commands manually.

- By default, handle commits, pushes, deploys, and release verification when the user asks for work that implies shipping.
- Only pause to ask when a required secret, approval, or external account action is genuinely missing.
- Keep the user informed of what was run and the outcome, but do not bounce routine execution back to them unnecessarily.
